data.description: This two-story home features three bedrooms (the primary is located on the main-level), two full bathrooms, a formal dining room, mudroom and a bonus room. The full basement has plenty of room for extra storage. This property offers a large fenced in yard, two-car garage, and an outbuilding for additional storage. Many updates including newer HVAC units (2022), and Hague Reverse Osmosis system. This home is spacious and ready for its next owner! Connect with a license REALTOR® to schedule a tour!
